<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text"><i>Atriplex spinifera </i>can sprout after fire and other disturbances and colonize from on- and off-site seed sources. Fire is not likely to be a strong natural impact to the stands; however, it may be a negative impact in areas with high annual non-native grass cover.</div>
